<style>
  h1, h2, h3, p {
font-family: sans-serif;
}
table {
  text-align: left;
}
</style>


<h1>Congrats <%= @winner_bid.user.name %>! You have just won the auction on <%= @winner_bid.npl.name %> NPL at Yield website</h1>

<p>You are receiving this e-mail to confirm that you are the winner of the auction on the following NPL:</p>

<hr>

<table class="table">
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <th>NPL Name:</th>
      <td><%= @winner_bid.npl.name %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th>NPL Seller:</th>
      <td><%= @winner_bid.npl.user.name %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th>Settlement price:</th>
      <td><%= number_to_currency(@winner_bid.value, unit:"R$", separator: ",", delimiter: ".") %></td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<hr>

<p><strong>You will receive an upcoming contact regarding the assigment contract and with the instructions for the payment.</strong></p>

<%= link_to "Get back to our website", root_url  %>

<p>Please do not hesitate in contact us if you do not recognize this action.</p>

<p>Kind regards,</p>
<p>The Yield team</p>

